a bomb thrown from a car damaged 
the home of a journalist and another blast caused panic at a soccer 
stadium authorities said 
no injuries were reported in either incident thursday no one 
claimed responsibility for the explosions and army col hector 
fonseca lopez said there were no arrests 
authorities said one bomb exploded in a vacant lot 200 yards 
