toilet paper employees get a recycling manual and they sign an 
agreement saying they will do their best to separate wastes 
although the amount will be small daily says the money received 
from recycling will be added to employee benefits the restaurant 
also uses a longdistance telephone company that donates 1 percent 
of its customers net bills to nonprofit environmental groups 
