delegates criticized his morning address one delegate said it had 
served only to raise the temperature of emotions 
the scheduled sixday meeting is being held in the same olivia 
sports hall where the union met for 18 stormy days in the autumn of 
1981 
communist authorities declared military rule to crush solidarity 
only two months later forcing the union into an eightyear battle 
to regain legal status and worker rights 
