she said this looking for new possibilities may start in this 
city 
norway which pumps 15 million barrels a day from north sea oil 
fields is the secondlargest oil exporter outside the opec oil 
cartel it also produces natural gas but has no way to deliver it 
to lithuania 
mrs prunskiene said her delegation would explore the 
