<TEXT>
do celebrities really care about spotted owls 
the ozone layer and rain forests or are they simply treehugging 
the cause of the week 
the evidence suggests that while numerous entertainers actor 
ed begley jr and singer jackson browne among them have adapted 
environmentally friendly living practices many others are slow to 
practice what they preach 
at a recent beverly hills benefit for the brazilian rain forest 
