agent michael ovitz were warned of the dangers of global warming 
and pollution 
the 1000 or so guests who dined on organic foods raised 12 
million for the environment most carpooled but the scores who 
didnt went for their limos which idled patiently stretching for 
blocks exhaust filled the evening air 
it was scarcely an isolated slip when hollywoods blueribbon 
environmental media association held its first organizational 
meeting at producer norman lears house ema founders arrived in 
mercedes bmws rollsroyces and other gasguzzlers 
producer ted field and wife susie who hosted the beverly hills 
rain forest benefit are longtime contributors to the natural 
resources defense council and charter members of ema they also 
have been known to fly to their spacious aspen home in a private 
jet 
its great celebrities are getting involved said bob 
